{"tid":1488412,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"First aid女義士謎題","createTime":"2019-08-19T15:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T15:54:42.000Z","uid":280853,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4f03997d2a96c28d1611a8e6f5a4d5ce01fae0c3","tid":1488412,"uid":280853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:18:55.000Z","msg":"811 女義士被射爆眼<br />\n<br />\n其實我睇直播同唔同片都認同first aid女義士係被布袋彈射中。<br />\n但一直以黎我都唔明點解唔告警察或報警比壓力警察<br />\n<br />\n唔報警原因：<br />\n1.報黎無用，狗查狗，狗狗相衛。<br />\n2.被人收買左，所以唔搞大件事<br />\n3.未完全好番，好番先再告同報警<br />\n4.女義士驚報左比狗搞，怕煩<br />\n5.告人唔一定贏，仲要錢。<br />\n<br />\n我一直諗唔明，報警同告狗都比到壓力，又收班唔報警姐係身有屎個啲人皮，點解唔行動？<br />\n<br />\n有無高人解答？<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 ！時代革命！"},{"pid":"9229261939b4a6654a0f9892d5f01330d72440cf","tid":1488412,"uid":206827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:19:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好意思 麻煩大家幫手投票定個死線<br />\n大家既訴求唔可以不了了之</span></span><br />\n死線投票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488382</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e35b301756fd216e0f2fa61d13281ac16644724c","tid":1488412,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:19:49.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eb7607e6ec41acec2914b20c56b61de0bc36b638","tid":1488412,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:19:53.000Z","msg":"心情未平復囉 ... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564906a32a8dda14265d5f6eda03d392249755aa","tid":1488412,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:22:37.000Z","